Ik hou ook van jou.

256
00:19:20.543 --> 00:19:21.943
Toe maar.

257
00:19:22.086 --> 00:19:23.486
Ik steun je.

258
00:19:23.838 --> 00:19:26.173
Ja. Oké.

259
00:19:30.302 --> 00:19:31.702
Met Vic.

260
00:19:32.888 --> 00:19:34.724
