393
00:27:38.415 --> 00:27:39.815
Oké.

394
00:27:41.293 --> 00:27:42.693
Ik zie je wel weer.

395
00:27:43.003 --> 00:27:44.403
Mooi.

396
00:27:48.383 --> 00:27:49.426
